bug.short_desc: Multiple page printing issue with OpenGrok if source code is long

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 4670 Screen show 1 page in print preview but it has muliple pages.
There is a multiple page printing issue with latest OpenGrok if we print source of code which has more pages.
Hi, I have its fixed also. Please suggest. you can contact me with the below email. 1. manoj.singh@igt.in 2. msinghb4u2gmail.com

Hello I'd be happy to accept your changes and take the fix for the css so the printing works properly
I think the cause is because of "css frames" which we use for top menu to always stay on the page
so if you have a patch with a fix, you can attach it here, I will just need an OCA# from you to accept them (OCA info & how to get it: http://hub.opensolaris.org/bin/view/Main/oca_faq )
the fix can be tricky and we even might end up in getting rid of the css frames (which probably wouldn't be that big of a deal, since I am sure in current html5 times we can replace this with something better working)
thnx L
